OL,11,G1800FRamsay's Hotel Hell
OL,12,     GVerindar runs her place like a
OL,13,     Gtyrant. Her employees are fed up
OL,14,     Gwith staying silent. So Gordon
OL,15,     Gtries to sprinkle his magic.
OL,16,     GHopefully the hotel won't stay so
OL,17,     Gtragic. _WorldPoetryDay
