OL,4,G1900FRamsay's Hotel Hell
OL,5,     GIf you're looking for a place to
OL,6,     Gsleep, at this resort you won't
OL,7,     Gget a peep. In these not-so-great
OL,8,     Gdigs, Brian hosts late-night
OL,9,     Ggigs. And his service would make
OL,10,     Gyou weep. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G2000FRamsay's Hotel Hell
OL,12,     GGordon visits a huge castle,
OL,13,     Gwhere the scenery certainly
OL,14,     Gdazzles. But sadly this citadel's
OL,15,     Gno fairy tale; it's Hotel Hell on
OL,16,     Ga massive scale. _WorldPoetryDay
