OL,11,     GThe Entertainer: Series two
OL,12,     Gstarts with Fran, ever keen to
OL,13,     Gdistract herself, taking up
OL,14,     Gpiano. Ever keen to delude
OL,15,     Ghimself, Bernard falls in love.
OL,16,     GAll Manny wants is a break.
OL,17,G0040FBlack Books
OL,18,     GFever: Fran can't sleep in the
OL,19,     Gheat. Bernard needs a girlfriend
OL,20,     Gto stop him staring. And Manny
OL,21,     Gcan't say what will happen if the
OL,22,     Gtemperature gets to 88 degrees.
